FX Daily Behavior
1. TIP service returns day specific FX rate based on the requested date. 
2. Weekend and holiday dates (e.g., Fri 20, Sat 21, Sun 22) return the same FX rate because FX market is closed; TIP returns the last available business-day rate. 
3. If a requested past date exceeds 2 years, TIP returns an error. 
If TIP has no rate for a specific day, system must decide: 
• Skip the day
• Use previous business day rate
• Or treat as missing (TBD)


